Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:05.97,ed-trans,,0,0,0,,The summer evening sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.06,0:23:12.77,JP_ED-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}鮮やかな過ぎ去りし日々
